Class Tcases

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cornutum.tcases.Tcases

    • Method Detail

      • getTests

        public static SystemTestDef getTests(SystemInputDef inputDef,
                                     IGeneratorSet genDef,
                                     SystemTestDef baseDef,
                                     GeneratorOptions options)
        Returns test case definitions for the given system input definition, using the given generator set and base test definitions. If genDef is null, the default generator is used. If baseDef is null, no base test definitions are used.

        The options are optional and may be null. See also getTests(SystemInputDef,IGeneratorSet,SystemTestDef).

      • getTests

        public static FunctionTestDef getTests(FunctionInputDef functionDef,
                                       ITestCaseGenerator functionGen,
                                       FunctionTestDef functionBase,
                                       GeneratorOptions options)
        Returns test case definitions for the given function input definition, using the given test case generator and base test definitions. The functionGen must be non-null. If functionBase is null, no base test definitions are used.

        The options are optional and may be null. See also getTests(FunctionInputDef,ITestCaseGenerator,FunctionTestDef).
